Tamerlan Tsaranev's 24-year-old widow 
has been under increased scrutiny ever since federal officials found 
radical Islamist materials on her laptop, including the al Qaeda 
magazine Inspire.

Investigators
 also found traces of explosive residue in the Cambridge, Massachusetts,
 home Russell had shared with her late husband and their 3-year-old 
